Description: An text string that informs the player of the "artifact heat" on the current expedition/mission. "{0]" is a placeholder for the "artifact heat" value, and "{1}" is a placeholder for a word that sums up the probability of the player being rewarded with a booster, e.g. "poor", "strong" etc.

Spanish.Translation: >Calor de artefacto en {0}, posibles resultados del potenciador:{1}

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: >Probabilidade de artefato em {0}, possíveis resultados de impulso:{1}

Japanese.Translation: > {0} でアーティファクトヒート、ブースター入手可能性:{1}

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: >寶物熱度為{0}，可能強化劑結果：{1}

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: >红晶热力值为{0}，获得强化剂可能性：{1}

name: InGame.ElevatorRide.ArtifactHeat_X_Result_Y
